I had a really good talk with someone who I admire. He said, “You have this light, don’t ever lose it or let anyone ever take it.” (Something like that) 😝 but it’s had me really thinking. 

I second guess myself and everything all the time. My whole life has always been hectic and not stable. Even with all the craziness that has happened in my life from good to bad, I’m really Fucking proud of myself. I’ve never been smarter, stronger, sexier, or braver then I have been right now. Some of you may not like me and that’s okay, but at the end as long as I like myself that’s all that matters. I love myself and again I’m so proud of who I’ve become. Thank you to the person who said this, you know who you are and I really appreciate you.

Moral of the story, keep going in life. You will have the hardest lows and the most incredible highs. That’s what life is supposed to be, a roller coaster of emotions, feelings, experiences. Enjoy the ride, stay true to your self! Be strong! Be brave! And always love yourself!!! 

Xo Heather.
